Huawei has launched a free premium service option for owners of its P20, P20 Pro, and P20 Lite smartphones. The Huawei Diamond VIP Service will be available to all customers who purchase these devices and includes a two-year warranty. The complimentary service plan includes: “The Huawei Diamond VIP Service for the P20 series is a superior service offering,” said Huawei. “The total value of this service, which is free for our P20 users, is just under R4,000.”